window.docContents[141].resolve({"/Basic-Types/Natural-Numbers/#nat-api-deceq":{"contents":"A decision procedure for equality of natural numbers, usually accessed via the DecidableEq Nat\ninstance.This function is overridden in both the kernel and the compiler to efficiently evaluate using the\narbitrary-precision arithmetic library. The definition provided here is the logical model.Examples:* Nat.decEq 5 5 = isTrue rfl* (if 3 = 4 then \"yes\" else \"no\") = \"no\"* show 12 = 12 by decide\n\nA decision procedure for non-strict inequality of natural numbers, usually accessed via the\nDecidableLE Nat instance.Examples:* (if 3 ≤ 4 then \"yes\" else \"no\") = \"yes\"* (if 6 ≤ 4 then \"yes\" else \"no\") = \"no\"* show 12 ≤ 12 by decide* show 5 ≤ 12 by decide\n\nA decision procedure for strict inequality of natural numbers, usually accessed via the\nDecidableLT Nat instance.Examples:* (if 3 < 4 then \"yes\" else \"no\") = \"yes\"* (if 4 < 4 then \"yes\" else \"no\") = \"no\"* (if 6 < 4 then \"yes\" else \"no\") = \"no\"* show 5 < 12 by decide\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009自然数\u0009API 参考\u0009比较","header":"20.1.4.5.2. 可判定的平等","id":"/Basic-Types/Natural-Numbers/#nat-api-deceq"},"/Build-Tools-and-Distribution/Lake/#zh-buildtools-lake-cli-h010":{"contents":"\n\n\n\n列出工作区中可用的 脚本。\n\n\n\n此命令运行工作区的 script（或指定的 package），\n将 args 传递给它。裸 run 命令将运行根包的默认脚本（不带参数）。\n\n打印 script 的文档注释。\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009Build Tools\u0009Lake\u0009命令行界面\u0009开发工具","header":"24.1.2.8.2. 脚本","id":"/Build-Tools-and-Distribution/Lake/#zh-buildtools-lake-cli-h010"},"/Elaboration-and-Compilation/#zh-elaboration-root":{"contents":"粗略地说，Lean对一个源文件的处理可以分为以下几个阶段：\n\n 解析\n\n解析器将字符序列转换为 Syntax 类型的语法树。\n  Lean 的解析器是可扩展的，因此 Syntax 类型非常通用。\n\n 宏展开\n\n宏是用更基本的语法代替语法糖的转换。\n  宏展开的输入和输出的类型均为 Syntax。\n\n 精化\n\n精化 是将 Lean 面向用户的语法转换为其核心 类型论 的过程。\n  这个核心理论要简单得多，使得可信的内核变得非常小。\n  精化还生成用于 Lean 交互功能的元数据，例如证明状态或表达式类型，并将它们存储在侧表中。\n\n 内核正在检查\n\nLean 的可信内核检查精化器的输出，以确保其遵循 类型论 的规则。\n\n 汇编\n\n编译器将详细的 Lean 代码转换为可以运行的可执行文件。\n\n\n\nThe Lean PipelinepipelineDiagram\n\n\n实际上，上述阶段并不严格地依次发生。\nLean 解析单个 command（顶级声明），对其进行详细说明，并执行任何必要的内核检查。\n宏展开是精化的一部分；在翻译一段语法之前，精化器首先扩展最外层存在的任何宏。\n宏语法可能保留在更深的层，但当精化器到达这些层时，它将扩展。\n精化有多种：命令精化实现每个顶级命令的效果（例如声明 归纳类型、保存定义、求值表达式），而术语精化负责构造在许多命令中出现的术语（例如签名中的类型、定义的右侧或要计算的表达式）。\n策略执行是术语精化的专业化。\n\n详细说明命令时，Lean 的状态会发生变化。\n新的定义或类型可能已保存以供将来使用，语法可能会扩展，或者无需明确限定即可引用的名称集可能已更改。\n下一个命令在此更新的状态下被解析和详细说明，并且它本身更新后续命令的状态。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考","header":"2. 精化和编译","id":"/Elaboration-and-Compilation/#zh-elaboration-root"},"/Functors___-Monads-and-___do___-Notation/Varieties-of-Monads/#zh-monads-zoo-state-h004":{"contents":"\n\nmonad StateRefT σ m 是一种专用状态 monad 转换器，当 m 是可以将 ST 计算提升到的 monad 时，可以使用它。\n它使用 ST.Ref 而不是纯函数来实现 MonadState 的操作。\n这确保了突变在运行时实际使用。\n\nST 和 EST 需要一个幻像类型参数，该参数与 runST 的多态函数参数一起使用以封装可变性。\n不需要将此作为变压器的参数，而是使用辅助类型类 STWorld 直接从 m 传播它。\n\n变压器本身被定义为 语法扩展 和 精化器，而不是普通函数。\n这是因为 STWorld 没有方法：它的存在只是为了将信息从内部 monad 传播到转换后的 monad。\n然而，它的实例是术语；保留它们可能会导致不必要的大型类型。\n\nAn auxiliary class used to infer the “state” of EST and ST monads.\n\nStateRefTStateRefT σ m 的语法接受两个参数：其精化器合成 STWorld ω m 的实例，以确保 m 支持可变引用。\n发现 ω 的值后，它会生成项 StateRefT' ω σ m，并丢弃合成的实例。\n\nA state monad that uses an actual mutable reference cell (i.e. an ST.Ref ω σ).The macro StateRefT σ m α infers ω from m. It should normally be used instead.\n\nRetrieves the current value of the monad's mutable state.This increments the reference count of the state, which may inhibit in-place updates.\n\nReplaces the mutable state with a new value.\n\nApplies a function to the current state that both computes a new state and a value. The new state\nreplaces the current state, and the value is returned.It is equivalent to a get followed by a set. However, using modifyGet may lead to higher\nperformance because it doesn't add a new reference to the state value. Additional references can\ninhibit in-place updates of data.\n\nExecutes an action from a monad with added state in the underlying monad m. Given an initial\nstate, it returns a value paired with the final state.The monad m must support ST effects in order to create and mutate reference cells.\n\nExecutes an action from a monad with added state in the underlying monad m. Given an initial\nstate, it returns a value, discarding the final state.The monad m must support ST effects in order to create and mutate reference cells.\n\nRuns an action from the underlying monad in the monad with state. The state is not modified.This function is typically implicitly accessed via a MonadLiftT instance as part of automatic\nlifting.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009函子、Monad 和  do  表示法\u0009单子的种类\u0009状态","header":"18.5.4.4. 来自可变引用的状态 Monad","id":"/Functors___-Monads-and-___do___-Notation/Varieties-of-Monads/#zh-monads-zoo-state-h004"},"/Interacting-with-Lean/#hash-print":{"contents":"#print 系列命令用于查询 Lean 以获取有关定义的信息。\n\nPrinting Definitions打印常量的定义。\n\n使用 #print 打印定义会将定义打印为术语。\n使用 策略 证明的定理在打印为项时可能会非常大。\n\nPrinting Strings将字符串文字添加到 Lean 的 消息日志。\n\nPrinting Axioms列出常量传递依赖的所有公理。有关更多信息，请参阅 公理文档。\n\nPrinting Axioms这两个函数各自交换一对位向量中的元素：def swap (x y : BitVec 32) : BitVec 32 × BitVec 32 :=\n  (y, x)\n\ndef swap' (x y : BitVec 32) : BitVec 32 × BitVec 32 :=\n  let x := x ^^^ y\n  let y := x ^^^ y\n  let x := x ^^^ y\n  (x, y)\n使用 函数扩展性、简化器 和 bv_decide 可以证明它们是相等的：theorem swap_eq_swap' : swap = swap' := by\n  funext x y\n  simp only [swap, swap', Prod.mk.injEq]\n  bv_decide\n由此产生的证明使用了许多公理：#print axioms swap_eq_swap'\n'swap_eq_swap'' depends on axioms: [propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound, swap_eq_swap'._native.bv_decide.ax_3]\n公理 swap_eq_swap'._native.bv_decide.ax_3 由 bv_decide 生成，表明本机代码用于将外部证明证书转换为 Lean 证明项。\n\nPrinting Equations命令 #print equations（可缩写为 #print eqns）显示函数的 方程引理。\n\nPrinting Equationsdef intersperse (x : α) : List α → List α\n  | y :: z :: zs => y :: x :: intersperse x (z :: zs)\n  | xs => xs\n\n#print equations intersperse\nequations:\n@[backward_defeq] theorem intersperse.eq_1.{u_1} : ∀ {α : Type u_1} (x y z : α) (zs : List α),\n  intersperse x (y :: z :: zs) = y :: x :: intersperse x (z :: zs)\ntheorem intersperse.eq_2.{u_1} : ∀ {α : Type u_1} (x : α) (x_1 : List α),\n  (∀ (y z : α) (zs : List α), x_1 = y :: z :: zs → False) → intersperse x x_1 = x_1\n它不打印定义方程，也不打印展开方程：#check intersperse.eq_def\nintersperse.eq_def.{u_1} {α : Type u_1} (x : α) (x✝ : List α) :\n  intersperse x x✝ =\n    match x✝ with\n    | y :: z :: zs => y :: x :: intersperse x (z :: zs)\n    | xs => xs\n#check intersperse.eq_unfold\nintersperse.eq_unfold.{u_1} :\n  @intersperse = fun {α} x x_1 =>\n    match x_1 with\n    | y :: z :: zs => y :: x :: intersperse x (z :: zs)\n    | xs => xs\n\n\nScope Information#where gives a description of the state of the current scope scope.\nThis includes the current namespace, open namespaces, universe and variable commands,\nand options set with set_option.\n\nScope Information#where 命令显示对当前 节范围 所做的所有修改，无论是在当前范围还是在其嵌套的范围中。section\nopen Nat\n\nnamespace A\nvariable (n : Nat)\nnamespace B\n\nopen List\nset_option pp.funBinderTypes true\n\n#where\n\nend A.B\nend\nnamespace A.B\n\nopen Nat List\n\nvariable (n : Nat)\n\nset_option pp.funBinderTypes true\n\n\nChecking the Lean VersionShows the current Lean version. Prints Lean.versionString.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009与 Lean 交互","header":"3.5. 查询上下文","id":"/Interacting-with-Lean/#hash-print"}});